      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "## Update post Community Guidelines update\r\n\r\nThis release was made to address the issues found with the new Obsidian plugin review tool.\r\n- There are no more dynamic `<script>` elements in the code base. This makes for a more trustworthy code base, as all code that is executed is visible in this repo\r\n- The code now includes the Syrinscape API code (this is to be able to eliminate the `<script>` blocks.\r\n- Various code style fixes\r\n\r\n### New feature\r\n- It's easier to distinguish between Moods (which replace all currently playing music and mood) and Music (which is additive).\r\n   - Moods are indicated with a `=` sign, and Music with a `+`. \r\n   - One-shots still have the play button\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/scooper4711/obsidian-syrinscape/compare/1.10.2...1.10.3",
